# Story v160-1-4 transition flag (Phase A1 yarnâ†’pnpm migration).
# Mimics yarn-1.x classic node_modules hoisting so transitive imports
# (`pg`, `js-yaml`, `knex`, `@medusajs/core-flows`, `@jest/globals`, etc.)
# resolve without forcing every implicit dep to be promoted to a direct one
# during this rebase sprint. Story v160-1-7 (or follow-up cleanup) audits
